    <item>
      <title>中国社交媒体如何应对特朗普的胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/how-chinese-social-media-is-reacting-to-trump-s-win-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四上午，唐纳德·特朗普的选举胜利成为中国社交媒体上的热门话题，微博用户讨论了这对中美关系意味着什么，并猜测埃隆·马斯克将在特朗普第二届政府中扮演什么角色。与特朗普和卡玛拉·哈里斯的命运相关的中国模因股票也占据了讨论的主导地位。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/how-chinese-social-media-is-reacting-to-trump-s-win-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 04:36:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的中国威胁让投资者青睐印度、日本股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/trump-s-china-threat-has-investors-favoring-india-japan-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于关税风险笼罩着中国资产，唐纳德·特朗普的选举胜利将改变亚洲三大股票市场的短期资金流向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/trump-s-china-threat-has-investors-favoring-india-japan-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 04:29:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走强之际，越南将越南盾固定汇率降至历史低位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/vietnam-sets-dong-fix-rate-at-record-low-amid-dollar-strength</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南将越南盾的参考汇率设定在历史最低水平，这为在美元飙升重创新兴市场的情况下越南盾进一步走弱奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/vietnam-sets-dong-fix-rate-at-record-low-amid-dollar-strength</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 04:26:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国可能如何回应特朗普的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/how-china-might-respond-to-trump-s-tariffs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国印度太平洋计划德国马歇尔基金会董事总经理邦妮·格拉泽表示，特朗普再次当选总统后，中国已准备好与美国加强战略竞争。她表示，如果特朗普征收关税，北京已经开发出新的反击手段，包括扩大对关键矿产出口的限制和出售更多美国国债。她在“彭博社：中国秀”上发表讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/how-china-might-respond-to-trump-s-tariffs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 04:11:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Circle：特朗普可能会让两党对加密货币产生兴趣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/circle-trump-may-bring-bipartisan-interest-in-crypto-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Circle 首席战略官兼全球政策主管 Dante Disparte 在唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国总统竞选后，对加密货币行业增添了乐观情绪。他在“彭博：中国秀”节目的“新加坡金融科技节”间隙与 Avril Hong 讨论了他对特朗普实际履行竞选承诺的期望。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/circle-trump-may-bring-bipartisan-interest-in-crypto-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 03:38:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：交易员考虑特朗普和美联储政策，多数亚洲股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者为唐纳德·特朗普第二次当选总统以及美联储预期的降息做准备，大多数亚洲股市跟随美国股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 23:21:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
